name: T.I.M.E. Dividend
description: What is the project about? Helping human beings attain that all important human right, freedom of time. Through passive income we make this ideal possible. What makes your project unique? We are the first and only fully tokenized crypto wallet in existence. 100% of wallet revenue is distributed to TIME holders in the form of PLS (or relevant native coin to a given blockchain) History of your project. We launched the first part of our project in November of 2021. We launched our multi-chain EVM wallet, November of 2022 on Android, iOS and Chrome. TIME Launched in May of 2023. Whatâ€™s next for your project? To continue to build out new features for our wallet, build our user base and thereby increasing dividends for TIME holders! What can your token be used for? There is no staking, delegating or locking up of TIME required. Simply hold TIME on your desired blockchain (in this case PulseChain) and earn passive income in native coin (in this case PLS). When a swap occurs within the InternetMoney.io wallet a fee is charged. 100% of that fee is paid to TIME holders. You can claim your dividends every block. There is no minimum or maximum hold times. Your TIME is completely liquid. We are truly working towards an ecosystem to help people live a freer life. Earning passive income without having to be obsessed with screens. Earn Passive Income. Free Your Time.
